snippet.title: Among the Trolls - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: First shown during the 505 Games Spring 2022 showcase, Among the Trolls is a brand new survival game set deep among the forests of Finland, where magic can still be found. It will  arrive in early access on PC later this year.
